data.description: Checkout this amazing 6-bedroom, 3.5-bath traditional home, nestled on a spacious corner lot in a highly sought-after neighborhood. Crown molding is throughout the home, adding an elegant touch. Downstairs living space features new luxury vinyl flooring, with stone fireplace.  Spacious master suite conveniently located downstairs; bathroom comes with dual vanity, luxurious jacuzzi tub, and separate shower.  The home has capacious walk-in closets and plenty of storage space throughout. The spacious bedrooms and game room on upper level, offers plenty of space for a large family and entertainment. The fifth bedroom has a floor lift and is prewired for media room conversion, providing endless possibilities. In addition, the home has a large backyard with covered patio! The property is strategically located less than a mile from golf course, restaurants, and shopping centers. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
